entries.femaleVariant: Welcome. What can I do for you?
Got a question about your security cams...
I'd like to discuss your partnership program...
Friend o' mine was here a week ago and left a briefcase.
I'm curious, what do your partnership programs look like? My company's considering expanding its insurance package to include psychiatric care.
entries.maleVariant: I'm just curious, what do your partnership programs look like? My company's considering expanding its insurance package to include psychiatric care.

entries.femaleVariant: By all means. We are always open to new opportunities.
Can I make an appointment with a patient?

I'm afraid that won't be possible. Contact with the outside world can impede our highly specialized treatment.
I'm afraid our head doctor wouldn't permit it.
Ah, fantastic. Could I get an information booklet about this place? Just wanna pass it on to HR.
entries.maleVariant: Fantastic. Could I get an information booklet about this place? Just wanna pass it on to HR.

entries.femaleVariant: One moment, I'll go get it for you.
I brought you the papers you requested.

Our security system is limited to the patients' level. Restricted to employees, only.
